113
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:37,060
I really like it.

114
00:06:38,490 --> 00:06:42,170
♪The heart is as fragile as glass♪

115
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:45,830
♪Longing always comes during the night♪

116
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:49,580
♪Tears at the corner of my eyes,
a trembling voice♪

117
00:06:49,580 --> 00:06:52,660
♪You walk right into my dreams again♪

118
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:55,980
♪Your love is a rare luxury♪

119
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:57,220
I'm now Mrs. Zhou.

120
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:05,520
♪All I can do is let it settle down♪

121
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:07,610
♪Back to zero♪

122
00:07:07,620 --> 00:07:09,580
(The proposal's already done.)

123
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:12,100
(So his next move would be...)

124
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:15,660
Uh…

125
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:18,060
The bathroom's...

126
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:19,500
Where is it?

127
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:21,540
I'll take you there.

128
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:22,940
Hey.

129
00:07:24,300 --> 00:07:25,140
No need.

130
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:26,900
I can find it myself.

131
