164
00:09:59,220 --> 00:10:00,060
A long time ago.

165
00:10:14,700 --> 00:10:15,690
Zhou Tingyan.

166
00:10:16,340 --> 00:10:17,740
Every new chapter

167
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:19,180
needs a new beginning.

168
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:24,860
I can do that.

169
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:45,500
